title: Modular Walkway Set
description: A modular walkway set suited for an industrial/sci-fi scene. Uses one 4k atlas for all parts in the set and can be configured in a large number of ways.
longDescription:
Spice up your industrial of sci-fi scene with this modular walkway!

This set consists of 23 different parts that allow for endless configurations while still looking structurally sound as long as one adheres to the measurements of the set. The atlas is also very forgiving when it comes to creating custom parts form the ones included in the set if one has the experience and software to do so. Also comes with a color map and a material setup that is used to apply a custom color to the painted parts of the metal.

This pack features: 
22 Easily modifiable parts. 
4096x4096 Texture atlas. 
Customizable material. 
Collisions for all included pieces. 
An example scene that shows how this pack is used and fits together (Smaller scene in the screenshots).
